modName: Arlana the Axe Maiden -Housecarl of Riften Iona Replacer-
summary: Updated V. 2.2 Arlana the Axe Maiden - Housecarl of Riften replacer (Replaces Iona uses female stance). She is available as a one handed warrior that will dual flurry or a two handed barbarian. I have options for essential and non-essential, calculated or auto-level on the main version. The You have to become Thane of Riften to acquire her services
